<seg id=1> China Becomes Leading Eiderdown Production and Export Country </seg>
</hl>
<p>
<seg id=2> Xinhua News Agency, Beijing, September 1st, Reporter: Zhou Liang.  Over the past ten years, Chinese eiderdown and its wares industry have developed rapidly.  At present, it is an important part of China's light industry, and together the annual export quantity and export quota  comprise half of the world's entire eiderdown trade.  It is highly appreciated in the international eiderdown market. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=3> The industry of Chinese eiderdown and products started its quick development in the mid-1980s, when the entire industry made use of the advantages of Chinese materials and human resources.  China focused on utilizing advanced techniques and equipment from abroad, and subsequently both the quantity and quality of the products improved dramatically. </seg>
<seg id=4> According to a statistics to date, China has had over 3 thousand eiderdown and ware process enterprises.  Among these, more than 600 operate on a large scale with over 300 thousand employees, and form annual produce capacity of more than 50 million, total annual production value reached RMB8 billion. </seg>
<seg id=5> Throughout the past ten years of market development, China has now become the leading eiderdown manufacture and export country in the world, annually exporting nearly 30,000 tons of  eiderdown, and over 20 million eiderdown rpoducts with a  total amount of US$820 million.  In addition, eiderdown clothing export accounted for more than 50% of the industry. </seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg id=6> According to the introduction, the quality of Chinese eiderdown products have been always steadily increasing. </seg>
<seg id=7> In the first half of this year, 56 eiderdown clothing enterprises were spot tested, and there are 47 business enterprises whose products are all qualified, 84% of the total. </seg>
<seg id=8> In the market competition, brands such as Jiangxi Yaya Duck, Beijing Yililan, Guangdong Glanz, Sichuan Tiange all enjoy good reputations. </seg>
</p>
